🛠️ TECH STACK (OPTIMIZED FOR IMMERSION & SCALE)
Frontend (Next.js + TypeScript)
* Rendering: PixiJS (WebGL-based, 60fps smooth).
* Physics: Matter.js (realistic collisions, gravity).
* UI: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui (clean, responsive).
* State: Zustand (lightweight, fast updates).
* Audio: Howler.js (crowd noise, commentary, effects).
Backend (Next.js API Routes + Socket.io)
* Real-Time Updates: Socket.io (live matches, transfers, notifications).
* API Proxy: Hide Bzzoiro API key, cache responses in Turso.
* AI Logic: Custom Node.js scripts (tactics, opponent AI).
Database (Turso)
* Schema: Users, Clubs, Players, Matches, Transfers, Careers, Physics Data (JSON).
* Caching: Turso’s edge network for low-latency data.
PWA (Progressive Web App)
* Offline Mode: Workbox (cached matches, player data).
* Push Notifications: Service Worker (match results, transfer offers).
Hosting (Render)
* Frontend: Static Site (Next.js SSR/SSG).
* Backend: Web Service (Next.js API + Socket.io).
* Database: Turso (external, edge-optimized).

